data.description: This gorgeous home, located in sought after amenity-filled Embrey Mill, is truly designed to elevate daily living. Zoned for Colonial Forge High School, it is just minutes to the new I95 HOV access on Courthouse Rd and around the corner from shopping and dining at Embrey Mill Town Center. You’ll love relaxing & greeting neighbors on the charming covered front porch! Inside, the home boasts beautiful hardwood floors, crown molding, and 9ft ceilings throughout the main level. A warm color palette seamlessly blends with the room's height, creating a welcoming and comfortable atmosphere. The main-level bedroom is thoughtfully designed with a Murphy bed, providing versatility for use as an office. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the living room to the elegant dining room.  The gourmet kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring granite countertops, upgraded stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and a spacious island with bar seating. A stylish backsplash, pendant lighting, and under cabinet lighting add refined touches to the ambiance. The butler's pantry, adorned with glass-front espresso cabinets and a granite countertop, serves as an excellent prep area for gatherings.  The family room, complete with a gas fireplace, invites cozy gatherings on cool evenings. The main floor also includes a convenient mudroom for a seamless transition when returning home. On the upper level you will find an exquisite primary suite with plush carpeting, tray ceiling, and a substantial walk-in closet. The en suite is luxurious, featuring a dual vanity, large soaking tub, a tiled shower with bench, and a second spacious walk-in closet.  The upper level offers three additional carpeted bedrooms with walk-in closets, including one with a private bath and two sharing a Jack ‘n’ Jill bath. The loft area provides additional flexible living space. Transform the lower level into your entertainment hub, featuring an expansive carpeted rec room with recessed lighting and a Sony surround sound system with speakers and multi channel receiver making this the ideal space for game and movie nights. The full kitchen is perfect for keeping snacks at the ready, and a Murphy bed and full bathroom offer a comfortable space for guests or as an in-law suite.   Notable utility features include air scrubbers on both HVAC systems and a humidifier. Your outdoor living space features a composite deck, perfect for dining al fresco. The flat rear yard has room for furry friends to play in or for you to design your dream garden. This home is located in an incredible community with walking/jogging/biking trails, community pool, dog parks, soccer fields, Bistro restaurant and so much more! Don’t let your dream home get away- make an appointment to see it today.
